sources.title: The King of the Mountains (1962 French Comedy) Lucile Saint-Simon, Claude Rollet, Jean Lefebvre
sources.description:
When bandits meet their match, the mountains aren't the only thing in for a wild ride
In the mountains, bandits use the gullibility of lost tourists to rob them. Unfortunately for them, one day they come across Jacques Dupont and two English girls...

Original title: Le Roi des montagnes (1962) AKA: Voleur de femmes
